byline.contributor: Choe Sang-Hun contributed reporting from Seoul, South Korea, and Chris Buckley from Beijing.
byline.original: By MAGGIE HABERMAN and DAVID E. SANGER

lead_paragraph: Mr. Trump takes office in less than three weeks, and a successful long-range-missile test would present one of his first big national security tests.
